<H3> <TI>   New Azerbaijani Offensive in Nagorno-Karabakh Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Azerbaijani Offensive in Nagorno-Karabakh Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2604154394 Yerevan SNARK in English 1046 GMT 26 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2604154394 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Stepanakert, 26 April (SNARK)--Trying to extend the 
combat line, the Azerbaijani side undertook an offensive today 
in the south-eastern direction. As SNARK was told in the press 
bureau of Karabakh Defense Army, nearly at 0600 26 April, the 
Azeri troops supported by armoured vehicles attacked the 
positions of Karabakh forces in the south of Martuninskiy 
region, as well as in the Fizulinskiy section. 

</TEXT>

