  [Text] Moscow, 29 Apr (ITAR-TASS) -- Vladimir Shumeyko, 
chairman of the CIS interparliamentary assembly, is to head an 
important peace-making mission to Nagorno-Karabakh. The 
ITAR-TASS correspondent was told this by informed sources in 
