  [Text] Chisinau BASAPRESS, 26/4/1994 -- The Sudan 
ambassador to Moldova, Faruq Mustafa `Ali, with permanent 
residence in Bucharest presented his credentials to President 
Mircea Snegur, states the presidential press service communique. 
The Sudan diplomat stated during the meeting that the people he 
represents respect the Moldovan people's choice expressed on 
February 27th. He called this "a choice to erect a democratic, 
independent and sovereign state." Snegur pointed out that 
