<H3> <TI>   Deputy Chief of Militia Department, Family Shot Dead </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Deputy Chief of Militia Department, Family Shot Dead </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2804144694 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1107 GMT 28 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2804144694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A source close to law enforcement bodies reported to 
INTERFAX that in the night of 28 April deputy chief of the 
Tajikabad regional militia department Idibek Salomonov together 
with his wife and two children was shot dead from a sub-machine 
gun in his house (Tajikabad is located in the Garm group of 
Tajikistan's regions in the Republic's north-east). 
  According to the source, the law enforcement bodies do not 
know anything about the motives of the murder. They are 
examining several versions, the results will be reported after 
the conclusion of the investigation. 

</TEXT>

