<H3> <TI>   Defense Cooperation Treaty With Estonia Signed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Defense Cooperation Treaty With Estonia Signed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MK2804120094 Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 28 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
