<H3> <TI>   Poll Shows Decline in Support for Most Parties </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Poll Shows Decline in Support for Most Parties </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2804154794 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 28 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
