  [Text] Bonn -- The Social Democratic Party of Germany 
[SPD] has called for sending civilian United Nations observers 
to the Kurdish areas in Turkey. This would help to protect the 
lives of threatened people more efficiently, Deputy Chairperson 
Heidemarie Wieczorek-Zeul told journalists in Bonn on Wednesday 
