  In addition, the Federal Government and the other 
governments 
of the European Union [EU] should increase pressure on the 
Turkish government. The association agreement between the EU 
and Turkey is a good means of doing this. The SPD politician 
emphasized that foreign policy must not be confined to 
"ingratiating oneself" with Turkey. 

