<H3> <TI>   Martinazzoli Resigns From Italian Popular Party </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Martinazzoli Resigns From Italian Popular Party </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3003130994 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1242 GMT 
30 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3003130994 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome RAI Televideo Teletext </F>
<F P=105>  Italian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] Mino Martinazzoli, the secretary of the Italian 
Popular Party has written a letter of resignation to the party 
chairman Rosa Russo Jervolino. [passage omitted] 
  His spokesman Marco Giudici confirmed that the resignation 
is 
official and irrevocable. Jervolino will hold a news conference 
at the party's headquarters at 1800. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

