<H3> <TI>   * Son of Kim Il-song Arrives as Ambassador </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    * Son of Kim Il-song Arrives as Ambassador </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P20561A Helsinki HELSINGIN SANOMAT in Finnish 13 Mar 94 p 5 </F>
