<F P=104>  Helsinki HELSINGIN SANOMAT </F>
<F P=105>  Finnish </F>


<TEXT>
CSO 

<F P=106> [Article by Unto Hamalainen: "North Korea's Leader Sends Son </F>
as Ambassador to Finland"] 
  [Excerpt] North Korean leader Kim Il-song's second son, Kim 
Pyong-il, arrived Friday [11 March] in Finland. Kim Pyong-il is 
his country's new ambassador in the Helsinki embassy. North 
Korea's embassy confirmed the envoy's arrival on Saturday. 
  The new ambassador will submit his credentials to President 
Martti Ahtisaari next Friday. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

