<F P=101> Inter-European Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Majority Vote Within Enlarged Council Approved </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Majority Vote Within Enlarged Council Approved </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR3103122494 Brussels Textline Database in English 30 Mar 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR3103122494 </F>
<F P=104>  Brussels Textline Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
